OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777579557
OL,3,CKobbie Mainoo signs new five-year
OL,4,Ccontract with United
OL,6,FKobbie Mainoo has pledged his long-
OL,7,Fterm future to Manchester United,
OL,8,Fsigning a new five-year contract that
OL,9,Fwill keep him at Old Trafford until
OL,10,F2031.
OL,12,FThe 21-year-old midfielder, born in
OL,13,FStockport and a product of United's
OL,14,Fyouth academy, has already made 98
OL,15,Fappearances and scored seven goals for
OL,16,Fhis boyhood club, including a
OL,17,Fmemorable strike in the 2024 FA Cup
OL,18,Ffinal victory over Manchester City.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
