OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777579557
OL,3,CKobbie Mainoo signs new five-year
OL,4,Ccontract with United
OL,6,FAfter a challenging start to the
OL,7,Fseason under former boss Ruben Amorim,
OL,8,Fwhen Mainoo's future at United
OL,9,Fappeared uncertain, the midfielder has
OL,10,Ffound a new lease of life under
OL,11,FMichael Carrick.
OL,13,FSince Carrick's arrival, Mainoo has
OL,14,Fbecome a regular starter and played a
OL,15,Fcrucial role as United climbed to
OL,16,Fthird in the Premier League and all
OL,17,Fbut secured Champions League
OL,18,Fqualification.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
