CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777579557
OL,3,CKobbie Mainoo signs new five-year
OL,4,Ccontract with United
OL,6,FFrom The Cliff, to Littleton Road
OL,7,F(academy facilities), to Carrington
OL,8,Fand ultimately Old Trafford, the
OL,9,Fmidfielder says his journey so far has
OL,10,Fbeen incredible.
OL,12,FMainoo said: " "Manchester United has
OL,13,Falways been my home; this special club
OL,14,Fmeans everything to my family,
OL,16,F"I relish the responsibility that
OL,17,Fcomes with wearing this shirt. The
OL,18,Fjourney so far has been incredible,
OL,19,Fand I have the privilege of living my
OL,20,Fdream every single day.
OL,26,@tD@POUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
