CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777579557
OL,3,CKobbie Mainoo signs new five-year
OL,4,Ccontract with United
OL,6,F"We can all feel the momentum building
OL,7,Finside the club. I am determined to
OL,8,Fstep up and play my role in helping
OL,9,FManchester United to regularly fight
OL,10,Ffor major trophies in the years ahead."
OL,12,FUnited's director of football Jason
OL,13,FWilcox praised Mainoo for his
OL,14,Fprofessionalism and impact as a role
OL,15,Fmodel for the academy.
OL,17,FWilcox said: "Mainoo is one of the
OL,18,Fmost naturally gifted young
OL,19,Ffootballers in the world,
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@gO]yD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
