FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777579557
OL,3,CKobbie Mainoo signs new five-year
OL,4,Ccontract with United
OL,6,F"We are delighted that Kobbie has
OL,7,Fextended his stay here and have full
OL,8,Fconfidence that he will develop into
OL,9,Fone of the best players in the world,
OL,10,Fready to play a pivotal role in a
OL,11,FManchester United team challenging for
OL,12,Fthe biggest honours."
OL,14,FMainoo's previous deal was set to
OL,15,Fexpire next summer, but his new
OL,16,Fcontract signals United's intent to
OL,17,Fbuild its future around the talented
OL,18,Fmidfielder.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@UO]
